# Vaelund Devlog — Post Format

Add new posts as `.md` files here. Filename doesn't matter — the `date` field in frontmatter is what counts.

Run `python3 scripts/generate-devlog.py` to generate the HTML pages.

## Frontmatter

```yaml
---
title: Your post title here
date: 2026-04-09
tag: progress  # or: feature, fix, lore, meta
excerpt: One sentence summary shown on the index page.
---
```

## Body

Write in the Vaelund voice — Brandon Sanderson + WoW lore. Direct. Plain verbs. Short sentences. No hedging.

See `/home/deck/dev/world/docs/STYLE.md` for the full style guide.
